issuance of the ordinance, the meeting can be held if the majority of members of the Constitutional Council are present.\n\nEarlier, the quorum for the meeting was considered to be reached only when the council Chairperson and four members were present.\n\nAmong the members of the council, the post of deputy speaker is currently vacant. In this case, the quorum for the meeting would have been reached only if all the other members were present.","title":"Writ filed at Supreme Court against Constitutional Council Ordinance - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/16/149299/","video":[]}
